ley KR</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2010-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>0743-7463</gtr:issn><gtr:outcomeId>doi_53d01a01a68723bb</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication><gtr:publication><gtr:id>371BCF08-A6ED-43FE-86AB-B41BC496877F</gtr:id><gtr:title>Giant amyloid spherulites reveal their true colours</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Soft Matter</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/6174d851e88487fed8422110a02b660f"><gtr:id>6174d851e88487fed8422110a02b660f</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Smith M</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2012-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:outcomeId>doi_53d02f02ff1571f1</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication><gtr:publication><gtr:id>EDB9D135-D523-4907-8BAB-55303B21068D</gtr:id><gtr:title>Electrostatics controls the formation of amyloid superstructures in protein aggregation.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Physical review letters</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/e3158421f6adbb16043a4ceababc5291"><gtr:id>e3158421f6adbb16043a4ceababc5291</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Foder? V</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2013-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>0031-9007</gtr:issn><gtr:outcomeId>doi_55f95e95e34a7028</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication><gtr:publication><gtr:id>8A838DF0-9D17-41D0-B4D0-CBC885555AFF</gtr:id><gtr:title>Factors affecting the formation of insulin amyloid spherulites.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Colloids and surfaces. B, Biointerfaces</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/d30ab37c6bf19dcf501f096719a94dce"><gtr:id>d30ab37c6bf19dcf501f096719a94dce</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Smith MI</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2012-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>0927-7765</gtr:issn><gtr:outcomeId>doi_53cfe9fe9f0c9295</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication></gtr:publications><gtr:identifiers><gtr:identifier type="RCUK">EP/H004939/1</gtr:identifier></gtr:iden